286
00:14:43,583 --> 00:14:46,016
I'll transfer him to the ICU.

287
00:14:46,051 --> 00:14:49,269
And I'll contact
the transplant team.

288
00:14:55,211 --> 00:14:58,946
Well, you're definitely still
pregnant, but I'm guessing

