00:15:36,769 --> 00:15:39,086
It's leaking severely.

301
00:15:39,122 --> 00:15:40,387
Mitral regurg.

302
00:15:40,422 --> 00:15:42,056
It's causing fluid to back up

303
00:15:42,092 --> 00:15:43,557
into her lungs.

304
00:15:43,593 --> 00:15:45,604
We have to, uh, get
her in surgery right away.

305
00:15:45,628 --> 00:15:46,906
I'm gonna book
an OR and scrub in.

306
00:15:46,930 --> 00:15:48,574
Whoa, wait, take
your foot off the gas.

307
00:15:48,598 --> 00:15:50,097
The regurg isn't emergent.

308
00:15:50,133 --> 00:15:51,749
The valve needs to be replaced.

309
00:15:51,784 --> 00:15:53,245
With the continued stress
of pregnancy, she could

