00:16:17,911 --> 00:16:20,539
We obviously
trust your judgment.

321
00:16:20,563 --> 00:16:21,857
What I think Mina's
trying to say is,

322
00:16:21,881 --> 00:16:23,464
we need to save Mom and baby.

323
00:16:23,499 --> 00:16:24,943
No, that is not
what I want to say.

324
00:16:24,967 --> 00:16:27,785
The mother is
priority number one.

325
00:16:27,821 --> 00:16:29,447
There is no choice
to be made, Mina.

326
00:16:29,471 --> 00:16:31,272
We save both baby and the mama.

327
00:16:31,307 --> 00:16:32,823
Adaku is a high-risk pregnancy.

328
00:16:32,859 --> 00:16:34,286
We need to get
our ducks in a row

329
00:16:34,310 --> 00:16:36,455
- before surgery, Mina.
- Thank you, Nic.

