00:16:48,007 --> 00:16:50,474
and we will repair the valve.

336
00:16:50,510 --> 00:16:53,143
And there is every
reason to believe

337
00:16:53,179 --> 00:16:55,307
it's going to be fine.

338
00:16:55,331 --> 00:16:57,915
If her condition
changes, page me.

339
00:16:59,502 --> 00:17:01,002
Look, if you are frightened,

340
00:17:01,037 --> 00:17:03,637
you are gonna transfer
that anxiety onto Adaku.

341
00:17:03,673 --> 00:17:07,058
The only thing we can do
now is show rock-solid support.

342
00:17:07,093 --> 00:17:09,509
And to restate the obvious,
Mina, I'm here for you.

343
00:17:09,545 --> 00:17:10,878
Okay?

