00:18:31,110 --> 00:18:32,576
He's a football player.

373
00:18:32,612 --> 00:18:33,939
Tried to self-treat
his back pain.

374
00:18:33,963 --> 00:18:36,097
Took too many.

375
00:18:36,132 --> 00:18:38,248
Ah, this was a...

376
00:18:38,284 --> 00:18:41,752
